text = "hii! this is the first build of OUROBOROS :)
it's still lacking MANY features, including buttons, switches, proper navigation, etc. despite this, I still hope you found it fun and intriguing! I promise it'll be more fleshed out next time.

I'd like to thank:
Arden, for being my rubber duck and moral support.
Mr robins, for teaching me most of the godot skills I have.
The metaphysical person of the Godot Stable Documentation, for saving my life.
The struggles of others that were resolved in the Godot Forums, so that I could succeed.

thanks for playing!!"
